text:
[Verse]
Under stars we glow bright
Dancing through the night
Feel the cool breeze flow
Life in lunar light

[Chorus]
Dance with the moon
Feel the world swoon
Heartbeat in tune
Dance with the moon

[Verse 2]
Shadows create dreams
Whispers in moonbeams
Eyes closed we fly high
Nights like endless streams

[Chorus]
Dance with the moon
Feel the world swoon
Heartbeat in tune
Dance with the moon

[Bridge]
Silver skies bring delight
Every move feels so right
Moonlight writes our song
In this moment so strong

[Chorus]
Dance with the moon
Feel the world swoon
Heartbeat in tune
Dance with the moon
title: Dance With the Moon
